ingredients: WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR), WATER, YEAST, SUGAR, EGGS, BUTTER (CREAM, SALT). CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: FERMENTED WHEAT FLOUR AND DOUGH EXTRACTS, POTATO FLOUR, DAIRY WHEY, WHEAT GLUTEN, SALT, MONO-AND DIGLYCERIDES, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORINGS, DOUGH CONDITIONERS (SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, ETHOXYLATED MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, CALCIUM SULFATE, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES, TRICALCIUM PHOSPHATE), NONFAT MILK, GUAR GUM, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), YELLOW CORN FLOUR, COLOR (TURMERIC, PAPRIKA, AND ANNATTO), SUCRALOSE, PROCESSING AIDS (ENRICHED MALTED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), SOYBEAN OIL).
